---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Automating Pipeline Delivery | Case Study">
  <div class="project-detail-bg">
    <div class="project-detail-card">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="back-button">&larr; Back to Case Studies</a>
      <div class="project-detail-content">
        <h1>How We Automated Pipeline Orchestration to Save 40+ Hours/Month</h1>
        <p class="summary">
          Manual data delivery was eating up engineering time and creating
          reliability problems. We built an automated orchestration system that
          handles daily delivery to multiple clients — hands-free.
        </p>

        <h2>The Challenge</h2>
        <p>
          The client was manually preparing and delivering data files to
          multiple pharma partners on a daily basis. Each partner had different
          security requirements, file formats, and delivery schedules. The
          process was error-prone and consumed 40+ hours of engineering time
          per month.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Built</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Modular Python DAGs (Directed Acyclic Graphs) to standardize ETL
            tasks across all clients.
          </li>
          <li>
            YAML-based pipeline configuration for easy modification, scaling,
            and onboarding new clients without code changes.
          </li>
          <li>
            Scheduled jobs (daily/historical) that join de-identified claims
            and tokenized tables to produce client-ready analytic datasets.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Security & Infrastructure</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Secure Cross-Account Delivery</strong>: Flexible
            authentication patterns to meet diverse client security needs:
            <ul>
              <li>
                AWS STS AssumeRole for temporary, least-privilege access
              </li>
              <li>
                Secrets Manager integration for secure key rotation
              </li>
              <li>
                Scoped IAM policies restricting access to specific S3 paths
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Automated Event Scheduling</strong>: AWS EventBridge
            triggers Lambda functions for reliable, unattended data shipments.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Results</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>40+ hours/month saved</strong> — daily automated, secure
            data transfer for multiple clients.
          </li>
          <li>
            New client onboarding reduced from days to hours — no code changes
            needed for new schedules or data splits.
          </li>
          <li>
            Improved compliance and auditability across all data deliveries.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="tech-stack-detail">
          <strong>Tech:</strong>
          <span>Apache Airflow (MWAA)</span>
          <span>Python</span>
          <span>YAML</span>
          <span>AWS Lambda</span>
          <span>S3</span>
          <span>EventBridge</span>
          <span>IAM</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .project-detail-bg {
      min-height: 100vh;
      width: 100vw;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.78), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)),
        url("/images/case_studies_tech.png") no-repeat center center;
      background-size: cover;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-top: 72px;
    }
    .project-detail-card {
      max-width: 830px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(25, 30, 55, 0.68);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 48px 40px 52px 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(130%);
    }
    .back-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #2997ff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-button:hover {
      color: #147bcd;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .project-detail-content {
      color: #f5f5f7;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2997ff;
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }
    .summary {
      font-size: 1.13rem;
      color: #f5f5f7;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #d2d2d7;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.18rem;
      color: #79bbff;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      padding-left: 1.2em;
    }
    ul li {
      font-size: 1.07rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.2em;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .tech-stack-detail {
      margin-top: 2.2rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem;
      background: rgba(41, 151, 255, 0.09);
      border-radius: 13px;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      color: #2997ff;
      font-weight: 500;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .tech-stack-detail strong {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-right: 10px;
      color: #147bcd;
    }
    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .project-detail-card {
        padding: 20px 8px 22px 8px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
